    "instructions": [
        "Heat the oil in a large casserole over a medium-high heat. Season the chicken and brown for 3-4 minutes on each side.",
        "Throw the chorizo, onion, garlic, celery and chilli into the pan and cook for a further 10 minutes, stirring occasionally.",
        "Add the wine or sherry and bring to the boil; add the chickpeas and tomatoes. Simmer and reduce for 5 minutes, then add the stock and courgettes. Simmer gently for 25 minutes. Scatter with the parsley. Serve with boiled potatoes or crusty bread."
